sources.title: Atlantic Rim | Full Movie | Action Sci-Fi Adventure
sources.description:
Atlantic Rim - When giant monsters crawl out of the Atlantic Ocean and attack the Eastern Seaboard the US Government is forced to trust a trio of mischievous soldiers, specialized in piloting gigantic robots, to defend America.
2013. Stars: Graham Greene, Anthony 'Treach' Criss, David Chokachi
